# Day 35 – Prompt Puzzle

## Objective

Built an interactive Prompt Puzzle application to learn Prompt Engineering through hands-on challenges.

## Features

- Domain & Difficulty Selection
- Build the Prompt Challenge
- Clean the Prompt Challenge
- Choose the Best Prompt Challenge
- Live Score Tracking
- Prompt Performance Report
- Replay with Random Scenarios
- Responsive UI

## Tech Stack

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Key Learnings

- Prompt quality directly impacts AI responses.
- Clear context and structured instructions improve output quality.
- Interactive learning makes prompt engineering easier to understand.

